subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Kayla McBride led the top-seeded Fighting Irish with 22 points against No. 16 Tennessee-Martin. Earlier, third-seeded North Carolina squeezed by No. 14 Albany.
